                        <h3 class="content">link roundup</h3>
                        <div class="content">
                           <div class="content">
                              <p>i've been slow with blogging lately cause of the mad rush with my project.  so here are a few links:<ul><li><a href="http://www.papierpixel.de/indexeng.html">paper pixels</a>: punchcards for light display.<br />
<li><a href="http://jee.manme.org.uk/gori/intro.php">GORI.node garden</a>: tangible social/privitized networking.<br />
<li><a href="http://www.sensacell.com/">sensacell</a>light emitting sensing modules.<br />
<li><a href="http://www.physorg.com/news4158.html>panasonic's tiny low-power bi-directional wireless module</a>: coin-sized wifi fun.<br />
<li><a href="http://www.cyberniklas.de/objekte/grafikdemo.htm">grafikdemo</a>: real spinning teapot jammed into an old commodore.<br />
<li><a href="http://www.siberart.com/home%20pages/home.html">the untitled project</a>: photos with all textual traces removed<br />
<li><a href="http://www.index2005.dk/Members/shisyku/bodyObject#">project unplugged</a>: solar cell silkscreened onto transparent organza.</ul></p>
                              
