<p><a href="http://www.ingo-maurer.com/">ingo maurer</a> designed this really flash LED table:<blockquote>278 white LEDs per table top, emitting light on both sides. 230/125 volts, 48 volts DC. Invisible Live Parts. There are tiny transparent wires embedded between the 2 sheets of glass, connecting the LEDs. The lights can be dimmed and even turned off if you suddenly want your LED table to look like a regular glass table again.</blockquote>so who wants to buy me one of these and let me augment it into a really hot interface?  anyone?</p>

